</table>
<table width="100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>·         <a href="#element_230044">1. PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: RSVP is available for Honors College lunch and screening of NACADA Webinar (11/20)</a>·         <a href="#element_230047">2. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Student Orientation Leader Applications due November 19th (Round 1 of Hiring)</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230050">3. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Spring 2016 ASP Courses from Academic Center for Excellence (ACE)</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230053">4. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: AANAPISI Initiative hosts Advising and Registration Workshops</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230056">5. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: ACE and FYI Drop-in Final Exam Prep (November 30th &#8211; December 4th) sponsored by ACE and the Office of First Year Initiatives</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230060">6. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: Next workshop at LARES is to prepare for finals on 11/19</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230066">7. Digest of Previous Weeks&#8217; Announcements</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_230075">8. UARC ADVISING WEEKLY UPDATES Web Submissions</a></td>
</tr>
