<td><strong><a href="https://illinois.edu/emailer/forward2/1979785?emailAddress=jvolpe@uic.edu&amp;orderId=4&amp;finder=&amp;constituentId=&amp;factsReferenceId=">PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: RSVP is available for Honors College lunch and screening of NACADA Webinar (11/20)</a></strong></td>
