<td><strong><a href="https://illinois.edu/emailer/forward2/1929068?emailAddress=jvolpe@uic.edu&amp;orderId=16&amp;finder=&amp;constituentId=&amp;factsReferenceId=">PROFESSIONAL DEVELOPMENT: Honors College is hosting lunch and a screening of NACADA&#8217;s webinar &#8220;Academic Advising for High Achieving Students: Strategies that Foster Resilience&#8221; on 11/20.</a></strong></td>
