<td>·         <a href="#element_219149">1. FOR ADVISORS&#8217; INFORMATION: MATH 180 Second Exam results have been distributed to students in the course.</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_219152">2. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: College of Education Undergraduate Programs is hosting info sessions and walk-in advising!</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_219155">3. SHARE WITH STUDENTS: LARES Midterm Check-Up Social is this Wednesday (10/28)!</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_219158">4. FOR YOUR REFERENCE: This Week&#8217;s other Advising Weekly Updates from 10-23-15 Email</a></p>
<p>·         <a href="#element_219177">5. Digest of Previous Weeks&#8217; Announcements</a></p>
