<td>Please share this information and/or <a href="https://illinois.edu/emailer/forward2/1829609?emailAddress=jvolpe@uic.edu&amp;orderId=10&amp;finder=&amp;constituentId=&amp;factsReferenceId=">flyer</a> with your students about TRIO&#8217;s event this week.</p>
<p>&#8212;<br />
Have you thought about the what, why, and when: when it comes to grad school? Still deliberating about your major and career path? What is it that you plan to do after graduation? How about your self-reflections?</p>
<p>Don&#8217;t worry!</p>
<p><strong>Graduate and Professional School Summit is here!</strong></p>
<p>Meet the experts for a dialogue regarding: Graduate School, College of Nursing, College of Pharmacy, College Business, College of Medicine, College of Dentistry, School of Public Health</p>
<p>Wednesday, October 28, 2015<br />
Student Center East<br />
Monarch Room<br />
12:00 &#8211; 2:00 p.m.</p>
